                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus/><p>Fol. 130rb: <span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt">Purchase note.</span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><div style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 14pt"><font size="2">Fol. 130rb: </font>&#4829;&#4757;&#4721;&#4961; &#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4824;&#4720;&#4925;&#4629;&#4936;&#4961; &#4704;&#4824;&#4632;&#4752;&#4961; &#4848;&#4867;&#4829;&#4635;&#4725;</span><span style="font-size: 10pt">[sic</span><span style="font-size: 10pt">]</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">&#4961; &#4657;&#4707;&#4875;&#4853;&#4661;&#4961; &#4824;&#4720;&#4643;&#4840;&#4902;&#4961; &#4676;&#4656;&#4961; &#4872;&#4704;&#4829;&#4961; &#4781;&#4941;&#4616;&#4961; &#4874;&#4846;&#4653;&#4874;&#4661;&#4961; &#4704;&#4757;&#4811;&#4840;&#4961; &#4708;&#4720;&#4961; &#4781;&#4653;&#4661;&#4722;&#4843;&#4757;&#4961; &#4808;&#4661;&#4632;&#4961; &#4608;&#4872;&#4653;&#4610;&#4961; &#4768;&#4853;&#4961; &#4680;&#4621;&#4683;&#4621;&#4961; &#4808;&#4661;&#4841;&#4632;&#4961; &#4608;&#4872;&#4653;&#4610;&#4961; &#4824;&#4657;&#4961; &#4624;&#4616;&#4675;&#4961; &#4781;&#4941;&#4616;&#4961; &#4874;&#4846;&#4653;&#4874;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4621;&#4848;&#4961; &#4645;&#4619;&#4660;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4829;&#4757;&#4721;&#4961; &#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4824;&#4640;&#4648;&#4678;&#4961; &#4808;&#4824;&#4936;&#4624;&#4678;&#4961; &#4808;&#4824;&#4720;&#4768;&#4872;&#4622;&#4961; &#4704;&#4645;&#4621;&#4899;&#4752;&#4961; &#4916;&#4901;&#4654;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4915;&#4813;&#4622;&#4661;&#4961; &#4813;&#4873;&#4824;&#4961; &#4616;&#4845;&#4777;&#4757;&#4962;</span></div> <p><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt">&#4808;&#4915;&#4915;&#4661;&#4610;&#4961; &#4768;&#4705;&#4752;&#4961; &#4676;&#4653;&#4622;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4768;&#4661;&#4704;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt">&#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4978;&#4808;&#4971;&#4961; &#4829;&#4757;&#4721;&#4961; &#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4770;&#4845;&#4931;&#4773;&#4961; &#4736;&#4704;&#4961; &#4779;&#4621;&#4773;&#4961; &#4608;&#4872;&#4653;&#4961; &#4824;&#4773;&#4757;&#4704;&#4616;&#4961; &#4969;&#4768;&#4619;&#4707;&#4961; &#4813;&#4829;&#4829; </span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt">[sic</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt">]</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt">&#4961; &#4813;&#4773;&#4721;&#4962;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"><div style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 10pt">[Fol. 130rb]: This book, which was written at the time of d&#228;&#287;&#287;azma&#269; Subagad&#601;s, was bought by qes&#228; g&#228;b&#228;z K&#601;fl&#228; Giyorgis&#160;with the money of the church; and the name of the village is &#704;Add Q<sup>w</sup>&#228;lq<sup>w</sup>al. The &#347;&#601;yyum of the village is the same &#7717;al&#228;qa K&#601;fl&#228; Giyorgis W&#228;ld&#228; &#346;&#601;llase. He who stole this book or he who deleted (its text) or he who&#160;took it away&#160;it shall be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul.</span></div> <p><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt">The Metropolitan is &#704;abun&#228; Qer&#601;llos. The payment for the book is 13 (B&#601;rr). This book may not be taken out to another&#160;place except&#160;wrapped in&#160;a&#160;wripping; this is forbidden.</span></p></q>
                           <p/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus/><p>Fol. 130rb: Note prohibiting to take the book out without textile&#160;secondary cover&#160;(?).</p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt"><font size="2">Fol. 130rb: </font>&#4770;&#4845;&#4923;&#4773;&#4961; &#4829;&#4757;&#4721;&#4961; &#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4824;&#4773;&#4757;&#4704;&#4616;&#4961; &#4969;&#4621;&#4709;&#4661;&#4961; &#4813;&#4873;&#4829;&#4961; &#4813;&#4773;&#4721;&#4961; &#4704;&#4645;&#4621;&#4899;&#4752;&#4961; &#4916;&#4901;&#4654;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4915;&#4813;&#4622;&#4661;&#4961; &#4770;&#4725;&#4653;&#4661;&#4817;&#4754;&#4961; &#4635;&#4741;&#4704;&#4653;&#4961; &#4824;&#4848;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4709;&#4653;&#4611;&#4757;&#4961; &#4874;&#4846;&#4653;&#4874;&#4661;&#4962;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"><p><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 10pt">[Fol. 130rb]: This book may not be taken out except (wrapped in) a vestment; this is forbidden by the authority of Peter and Paul. Do not forget me,&#160;the&#160;community of D&#228;br&#228; B&#601;rhan Giyorgis.</span></p></q>
                           <p/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Fol. 2v. Exercise in writing: the Trinitarian doxology (incomplete).&#xD;
- Fol. 8v, in the upper margin. Crude note.&#xD;
- Fols. 13r, 39r, Corrections or omissions written in the upper margin.&#xD;
- Some portions of the text (mainly kǝśtätat) are written in compressed script (s. fols. 30vb–31rb, 49vb–50ra, 54rb–54va, etc.).</item>
